Sellenium class05

--------------Radio Button---------------
we can select one radio button at a time

isDisplayed-->boolean
checks if the particular webElement is displayed/present on the page or not

isEnabled()-->boolean
checks if you can select that radio btn or not

isSelected()-->boolean
it tells weather the particular btn is selected or not


***********************Drop Downs****************************
there are two types of drop downs
1.Single Select
2.Multi Select

1 Single Select
Method 1:
click on the drop down
and then click on the option

Method 2:
Using a Select class
   there is  acondition in order to use select class
   we need to make sure that our drop down has a select Tag.

   if we use select class we can select in three different methods
   1.By index
   2.By visible text
   3.By value

